<title>USA: RESEARCH ALERT - Avant! cut to neutral.</title>
<headline>RESEARCH ALERT - Avant! cut to neutral.</headline>
<text>
<p>-- Morgan Stanley said it downgraded Avant! Corp to neutral from outperform.</p>
<p>-- shares plunged 11-7/8 to 12-5/8.</p>
<p>-- on Monday, the Santa Clara County, Calif. district attorney's office said it filed felony charges against Avant!, its president and other senior officials for allegedly stealing Cadence Design Systems Inc technology.</p>
